defaultWritten Submission from defaultGeneWatchdefault UKdefault&#xa0;
default&#xa0;
defaultGeneWatch
default UK is a not-for-profit organisation, established in 1998, which aims to ensure that genetic science and technologies are used in the public interest. The main focus of our response is the potential value and contribution of science and GM technology to UK food security and the need to consider alternative approaches.
